As I was reading, I noticed some minor issues with spag and it was slowly building towards something, but I didn't know what. Then Test #5 comes around the cornerdang! Then Test #6 is even worse! I feel kind of bad for the robot, but still don't know why he is such an ass to Arelli. But of course, it attempts to be a non-violent nuisance as much as possible.

The pacing overall was quite good and the execution of the story was great.

+1

